name: Pyrocms-facebook-photo-gallery-widget
body:
PyroCMS-Facebook-Photo-Gallery-Widget
=====================================

PyroCMS Facebook Photo Gallery Widget
This PyroCMS widget allows you to display facebook Photo Gallery from a user or page in a widget area such as a sidebar, you may have multiple instances of the widget which use the same cached feed.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
